OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1784571506
OL,3,CWoman charged with murder after 75
OL,4,Cyear old man found dead
OL,6,FA 49 year old woman has been charged
OL,7,Fwith murdering a 75 year-old pensioner
OL,8,Ffound dead in Bolton.
OL,10,FGreater Manchester Police said
OL,11,FSamantha Nuttall of Bradford Street in
OL,12,FBolton is in custody and will appear
OL,13,Fat Manchester and Salford Magistrates'
OL,14,FCourt on Monday 20 July.
OL,16,FThe man was discovered by officers who
OL,17,Fwere called to a property in Ormrod
OL,18,FStreet on Friday 17 July at about 8am.
OL,20,FHe was pronounced dead at the scene.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
