OL,3,CWoman charged with murder after 75
OL,4,Cyear old man found dead
OL,6,FFormal identification of the man has
OL,7,Ftaken place and his next of kin have
OL,8,Fbeen informed.
OL,10,FDetective Inspector Louise Kelly said:
OL,12,F"I would like to express my deepest
OL,13,Fcondolences to the victim's family and
OL,14,Floved ones as they navigate through
OL,15,Fthis loss. They will continue to be
OL,16,Fsupported by our specialist officers
OL,17,Fduring this difficult time."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
