CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1784571506
OL,3,CWoman charged with murder after 75
OL,4,Cyear old man found dead
OL,6,F"It is our priority to obtain some
OL,7,Fanswers regarding the full
OL,8,Fcircumstances of this tragic incident,
OL,9,Fand we are appealing for information
OL,10,Ffrom the public to help us progress
OL,11,Four investigation."
OL,13,F"Our Major Incident Team have launched
OL,14,Fa murder investigation and are
OL,15,Fcontinuing to pursue multiple lines of
OL,16,Fenquiry to establish the full
OL,17,Fcircumstances."
